{"title":"腊月","authors":["鲁谷风"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":1,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"腊月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安徽繁昌县　鲁谷风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三月春光，七月流火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九月金风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孕育了一个，香喷喷的腊月。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酿蜜的夜，孩子嘴馋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人不困。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灶膛里，惬意的火苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把农家瑞气烧红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年的冬米糖，好香好脆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石磨咿咿呀呀甜了嗓音！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡村大道上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泛着欢腾的溪流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽地又是几声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上梁的鞭爆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸响青靛的黎明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几个拾粪的老头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扳着指头："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪家攒钱买瓦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪家新屋落成……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腊月，一岁之末，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒冷和温馨的交替，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地冬眠的苏醒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们还来不及解开衣扣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春姑娘就已兴冲冲地串村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}